snippet.title: Best VGM 754 - Romancing Saga: Minstrel Song - A Challenge to God ~Four Guardian Kings Battle~
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 289 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ekiz0YMNp7A
Best VGM 626 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cYV7Ph-qvvI

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation 2
Romancing SaGa: Minstrel Song
A Challenge to God ~Four Guardian Kings Battle~
Tsuyoshi Sekito
